<text top="679" left="90" width="69" height="19" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="721" left="122" width="415" height="14" font="1">Maintenance of peace and security and post-conflict peace-building</text>
<text top="757" left="153" width="594" height="14" font="1">Disarmament, demobilization and reintegration of ex-combatants in a peacekeeping environment</text>
